</style><p>经营Horo Live Production的Cover Co.，Ltd。正在促进<strong>UGC</strong> （用户生成的内容）和粉丝游戏，并通过推出该品牌的二级创意游戏<strong>Holo Indie</strong>来支持支持。我们正在这样做。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="awDbi31JBb"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/hololive-production-fan-made-game-holo-break-to-be-released-in-march/">Holo Live Production的粉丝游戏“ Holo X Break”于三月发布</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“ Holo Live Production的粉丝 - 制作游戏“ Holo X Break” March发布” -P2Y.JP" src="https://p2y.jp/hololive-production-fan-made-game-holo-break-to-be-released-in-march/embed/#?secret=U1CKJ2kdoh#?secret=awDbi31JBb" data-secret="awDbi31JBb" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="9ANzQhBtKW"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/cover-established-guideline-for-secondary-game-creation-launched-holo-indie-brand/">涵盖了次要创意游戏，也推出了Holo现场游戏品牌“ Holo Indie”的指南</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="Holo Live的游戏品牌“ Holo Indie”也推出了次要创意游戏的指南。" src="https://p2y.jp/cover-established-guideline-for-secondary-game-creation-launched-holo-indie-brand/embed/#?secret=1tWEpUFEtn#?secret=9ANzQhBtKW" data-secret="9ANzQhBtKW" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="u8IOGqcx37"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/hololive-production-fan-made-game-holocure-to-be-released-on-ste